item.title: [+1058] YouTubers Getting Suspended Due to False Copyright Claims
item.description: Vandals have struck YouTube with false DMCA claims. Since YouTube's policy is to suspend first and ask questions later, flagged videos are removed before they are investigated. It's this course of action that has lead to many gaming-related channels such as Chuggaaconroy, TheArchfiend and NintendoCapriSun being unjustly suspended.
